}}'''瑪拉工藝大學'''（Universiti Teknologi MARA，簡稱UiTM）是一所位于[[马来西亚|马来西亚]][[莎阿南|莎阿南]]的[[公立大學|公立大學]]，該大學只面向[[馬來西亞土著|馬來西亞土著]]招生<ref>{{Cite news|title=UiTM remains for Malays, Bumiputera|url=https://www.nst.com.my/news/nation/2019/01/449451/uitm-remains-malays-bumiputera|accessdate=2021-03-08|archive-date=2021-02-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210208175157/https://www.nst.com.my/news/nation/2019/01/449451/uitm-remains-malays-bumiputera|dead-url=no}}</ref>。大學成立于1956年<ref>{{cite conference |first=Choo Hong |last=Loo |title=The evolution of distance learning and its contribution to the accounting profession in Malaysia:A historical perspective |conference=International Conference on Accounting Studies |date=17 August 2015 |location=Johor Bahru |url=http://www.icas.my/download/icas_2015/232-ICAS2015_Loo%20Choo%20Hong.pdf |access-date=7 February 2016 |archive-date=2017-09-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170912224903/http://www.icas.my/download/icas_2015/232-ICAS2015_Loo%20Choo%20Hong.pdf |dead-url=no }}</ref>。该大学由一个主校区和34个分校区组成<ref>{{Cite web|title=Information for Applicants|url=https://study.uitm.edu.my/index.php/information-for-applicants|accessdate=2021-02-04|work=study.uitm.edu.my|language=en-gb|archive-date=2020-08-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200806181529/https://study.uitm.edu.my/index.php/information-for-applicants|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=UiTM insists on retaining 'Bumiputera only' policy|url=https://www.freemalaysiatoday.com/category/nation/2019/01/11/uitm-insists-on-retaining-bumiputera-only-policy/|accessdate=2021-02-04|author=Bernama|date=2019-01-11|work=Free Malaysia Today (FMT)|language=en-US|archive-date=2019-02-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190203213147/https://www.freemalaysiatoday.com/category/nation/2019/01/11/uitm-insists-on-retaining-bumiputera-only-policy/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

==== 校区 ====
{{As of|2014|June}}，玛拉工艺大学在7个州属设有自治校区，分别为玻璃市、槟城、霹雳、登嘉楼、彭亨、马六甲和砂拉越。<ref>{{cite news |author=<!--Staff writer(s); no by-line.--> |title=PM: UiTM campuses to get autonomy status |url=http://www.thestar.com.my/news/nation/2015/04/12/pm-uitm-campuses-to-get-autonomy-status/ |newspaper=The Star Online |location=Kuala Lumpur |date=12 April 2015 |access-date=8 February 2016 |archive-date=2019-03-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190306111713/https://www.thestar.com.my/news/nation/2015/04/12/pm-uitm-campuses-to-get-autonomy-status/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>这与所有州校区最终都将获得自治管理级别的愿景是一致的，并赋予了每个校区有自己的创造力和提高了校区及其学生在各个领域的成就。这些自治校区的一个重要特征是能够举办自己的校内会议和仪式，而大多数行政决策将不受旗舰校区管理。 
